Features:

    * keep track movies you watched
    * mark movies as "like/didn't like"
    * mark movies as "to watch"
    * follow what your friends are watching
    * get recommendations based on what your friends liked and you didn't watch

Movie metadata:

    * title (English and original)
    * year
    * cover image
    * director
    * genre(s)
    * running time
    * main cast
    * link to trailer
